body: "The current repository passes duplication and coverage gates but several test modules have become books. Large spec files increase agent context cost, hide duplicated setup below the current clone threshold, and make focused failures harder to isolate. This item is organizational only: preserve every assertion and behavior while splitting by coherent scenarios and extracting shared fixtures when repeated setup is proven. Coordinate with pm-kb5h folder-density tranches so each file moves at most once."
